WEBVTT

00:00:00.750 --> 00:00:05.750
Everyone wants a happy family life.

00:00:05.750 --> 00:00:27.960
Realistically, though, even a husband and a wife who truly love each other will have some problems.

00:00:27.960 --> 00:00:31.960
You may wonder, what is the key to family happiness?

00:00:31.960 --> 00:00:42.729
The Bible says, happy are those hearing the Word of God and keeping it.

00:00:45.520 --> 00:00:51.520
Would you like to know how God's Word, the Bible, can help you have a happy family life?

00:00:51.520 --> 00:00:58.570
To find out, read the brochure, your family can be happy.

00:00:58.570 --> 00:01:05.569
You can download it free of charge from JW.org or you can obtain a copy from any of Jehovah's Witnesses.
